Mon Mar 23 15:49:42 UTC 2026 - Gakuto Furuya <g.furuya@gaato.net>

- ExcludeArch armv7l: rustc runs out of memory during LTO linking
  of llama-cpp on 32-bit ARM (670 s OOM in OBS builder)
