  to Suggests (tools are standalone static binaries)
- Use wildcard globs for icon file listing in %files
- Add cargo_audit source service
- Add %license to tools subpackage
- Use fcitx5 RPM macros in %files
- Add BuildRequires: hicolor-icon-theme

